OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening, with outbreaks of rain moving
OL,7,Fup from the south. The rain will
OL,8,Fcontinue to push northwards overnight
OL,9,Fand will become heavy at times, which
OL,10,Fcould lead to some difficult
OL,11,Ftravelling conditions. A mild night
OL,12,Facross the region.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FA cloudy start with outbreaks
OL,15,Fof rain, this locally heavy at first.
OL,16,FThe rain clearing by the afternoon,
OL,17,Fwith skies brightening. However, a few
OL,18,Fshowers may then also develop.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
